author: Epic Games
description:
Where Winds Meet is an epic open-world action-adventure RPG rooted in the rich legacy of Wuxia.
Join us for the exclusive trailer debut of "Where Winds Meet" at the 2025 Tokyo Game Show.

Embark on an unforgettable adventure in the enchanting world of Jianghu as the Young Wanderer. Explore the vast open world, engage in thrilling battles, and uncover the secrets of your past.
 
Wishlist now on the Epic Games Store! https://epic.gm/wwm
title: Where Winds Meet | Official Tokyo Game Show Trailer
